{"tid":344203,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［終極毒撚］一個人去海洋公園會點","createTime":"2017-08-02T06:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T09:18:22.000Z","uid":30831,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b0391432c620dd1b473b0da16a3625f45a691bd","tid":344203,"uid":30831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:15:28.000Z","msg":"小弟就黎生日 由細到大都係叫個pizza/蛋糕係屋企食就算 食唔哂放雪櫃第二日食埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年想開心下 自己去海洋公園 有啲野都想去玩下 同埋去睇水族館靜下心 但感覺實在係太毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過好似已經冇乜好選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實想問有冇經驗人士分享下 實際去到係喜定悲 我總覺得自己會瘋狂感受到孤獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔去慶祝下會更加悲傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有無其他生日一個人好去處<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369e60696cd5f8429b74e64efc896c7a04be15ab","tid":344203,"uid":5827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:35:38.000Z","msg":"迪士尼"},{"pid":"64e4460e8fdea793533081d7d2a0fa5e86ffa966","tid":344203,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a24dce806011525a062fb248d2920d0d98b514","tid":344203,"uid":103215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:40:30.000Z","msg":"搵個同日生日既一齊去"},{"pid":"3f07ed2efe4b7c74501bc0ceb63759220fcc6fe2","tid":344203,"uid":45627,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:43:16.000Z","msg":"試過自己一個去, 不過唔係生日<br />\n整體感覺係開心同幾爽嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我嗰陣就瘋狂玩過山車, 碰碰車同睇雪狐<br />\n冇人催不知幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐘意玩幾多次睇幾耐都得<br />\n上山落山都坐攬車睇風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過唯一不足係掟中公仔得自己high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96580d51672dd5bf0df004a915f9cf957ac8162c","tid":344203,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:47:39.000Z","msg":"生日搵個fd一齊去真係咁難咩？<br />\n<br />\n話自己去個d 唔該唔好再呃自己好開心啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f965dc0ac2470fd79eb40c8ec4967114b70bf0","tid":344203,"uid":30831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生日搵個fd一齊去真係咁難咩？<br />\n<br />\n話自己去個d 唔該唔好再呃自己好開心啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廢青左一年 真係一粒fd都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5051458451d13f10dc69b55c20f7d35005db7b3f","tid":344203,"uid":35504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:52:56.000Z","msg":"有咩點 咪同平時自己行街差唔多<br />\n自己接受到就得"},{"pid":"a01ee7c4f78b53ddb6aa33f40d714fc67eebdcad","tid":344203,"uid":30831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:53:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過自己一個去, 不過唔係生日<br />\n整體感覺係開心同幾爽嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我嗰陣就瘋狂玩過山車, 碰碰車同睇雪狐<br />\n冇人催不知幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐘意玩幾多次睇幾耐都得<br />\n上山落山都坐攬車睇風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過唯一不足係掟中公仔得自己high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最驚就係排隊既時候人地一pair pair 自己on99 工作人員見到我眼望望 一個人坐哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee46392e34177daca520a4a3355f6a68516f23a","tid":344203,"uid":12741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:05:47.000Z","msg":"建議唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇得出你本身就sad<br />\n<br />\n一個人無mood實好快走